  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 开头与设定",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_1416-1443",
          "range": "1416-1443",
          "rangeStart": 1416,
          "rangeEnd": 1443,
          "markText": "小说的核心困境必须重要到将某个人的一生彻底颠覆的程度。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1722988898,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-08-07 08:01:38",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1416&rangeEnd=1443",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1416&rangeEnd=1443"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_7843-7879",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7843-7879",
      "markText": "记住：如果在第一章壁炉台上出现了一块口香糖，那到最后它必须引发了什么事。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7843&rangeEnd=7879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7843&rangeEnd=7879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_1416-1443",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1416-1443",
      "markText": "小说的核心困境必须重要到将某个人的一生彻底颠覆的程度。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1416&rangeEnd=1443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1416&rangeEnd=1443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_4313-4378",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4313-4378",
      "markText": "对角色了如指掌是你的职责，要尽量少与读者分享太多记忆，“要尽量少”的意思其实是“不要”。作为写作者，你为读者提供的服务是：讲故事。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4313&rangeEnd=4378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4313&rangeEnd=4378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_4_487-504",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "487-504",
      "markText": "作者的职责只此一个：让读者看下去。",
      "totalCount": 253,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_10_6488-6564",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6488-6564",
      "markText": "主角在前三章都不应该出现自慰或者色眯眯地盯着陌生人看的情节。读者自然明白凡人都有欲望需要满足，但如果一上来看到的就是这回事，读者只会觉得角色猥琐又恶心。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6488&rangeEnd=6564",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6488&rangeEnd=6564"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_4616-4673",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4616-4673",
      "markText": "找出一个核心动作场景，以正在进行中的情景作为小说的开端，让你的角色在激烈的冲突中首次出场，以此迅速抓住读者注意力。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4616&rangeEnd=4673",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4616&rangeEnd=4673"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_3_1449-1499",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1449-1499",
      "markText": "如果读一读史蒂芬·金的《谈写作》就有用的话，那我们人人都能写出引人入胜的通俗小说，且能登上畅销榜单。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1449&rangeEnd=1499",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1449&rangeEnd=1499"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_5672-5743",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5672-5743",
      "markText": "如果奇普除了欣赏热带岛屿的神奇景致什么也没做，那这个地点不过就是个枝繁叶茂的等候室——再说了，那些枝叶读者早就在探索频道看过了，还是高清的呢。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5672&rangeEnd=5743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5672&rangeEnd=5743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_6_1909-1983",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1909-1983",
      "markText": "值得被创造出来的问题也值得放上一阵，从而足以让读者为之心生牵挂。大多数问题都值得一直放到结尾处，所有悬念被巧妙地收到一处，在最后达到激动人心的高潮。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1909&rangeEnd=1983",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1909&rangeEnd=1983"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_6_3464-3551",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3464-3551",
      "markText": "不要向你的读者保证一切都会安然无恙。有时候哪怕主角流露出一丝自信都会暗示读者大团圆结局必将出现。最好要让主角觉得几乎没有胜算——然而他依然下决心去尝试，即便要赌上自己的性命。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3464&rangeEnd=3551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3464&rangeEnd=3551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_4_1399-1431",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1399-1431",
      "markText": "展现的场景是主角看向窗外，默默思索那些作者没空放入正文的哲学难题",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1399&rangeEnd=1431",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1399&rangeEnd=1431"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_10_2656-2737",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2656-2737",
      "markText": "道德败坏的拜金女给了乞丐二十美元的情节会吸引我们。终日为人权奋斗的律师前去动物收容所当志愿者，或在赶往法庭的路上停下来给了乞丐二十美元，这样的安排只会让我们想吐。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2656&rangeEnd=2737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2656&rangeEnd=2737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_6_8698-8728",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8698-8728",
      "markText": "好办法是一部小说只留一个梦境，等到最终修订时回头也把它删了。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062446&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8698&rangeEnd=8728",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b0f322a0813ab7ee4g0167e1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8698&rangeEnd=8728"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062446_5_5446-5503",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5446-5503",
      "markText": "曾经有个时期，有本书的内容纯粹是作者从远方回来后所写的异国见闻，书卖得不错。这位作者叫马可·波罗，那时是十三世纪。",
